 sense that\nfor both galaxies, the more distant clusters have larger Q values. We also paid\nparticular attention to the effects of contamination by non-member field stars\nand its consequences finding that field star decontamination is crucial for\nthese kinds of studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2022 18:13:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-20"}
