o resembles the\nperiastron encounters of $\\eta$ Carinae prior to its Great Eruption and the\nerratic pre-SN eruptions of SN 2009ip. This similarity and the onset of\neruptions in the past decade hint that AT 2016blu may also be headed for a\ncatastrophe, making it a target of great interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2022 18:38:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 May 2023 22:52:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-19"}
