 scheme to compute the viscous forces\nas well as the momentum advection method were enhanced with a cache- and memory\nusage optimization. An overall performance gain of up to 33% was obtained for a\nrepresentative test case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2022 18:51:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2022 09:35:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-22"}
