r asymmetric\nconnection configurations with armchair-edged leads, we found that though the\nthermopower is almost intact, a remarkable reduction of the electronic thermal\nconductance can lead to a notable improvement in the figure of merit. Our\nresults suggest phosphorene nanorings as promising candidate nanostructures for\nTE applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 14:08:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
